#~| "created and added to the list."
#~ msgid ""
#~ "If a name is entered that is not yet known to &kmymoney; you will be "
#~ "asked if you want to create a new category record. If you do not wish to "
#~ "do so, then the field will be blanked. Otherwise, the record will be "
#~ "created and added to the list."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Αν το όνομα που έχετε εισαγάγει δεν είναι γνωστό ακόμα στο &kappname; θα "
